- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new approach to capture the meaning of sentences, which is a fundamental task in AI. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also possible as the paper deals with text classification, which is a subfield of IR. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still possible as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach for text representation learning.
